  "title": "今日开源（2025-10-13）：LLaVA-OneVision 开源，图像训练降本提效，多模态基准性能超 Qwen2.5-VL",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247499729&idx=1&sn=5424ae30b1c911687cb0dccd4da3e7d0",
  "date": "2025-10-13 10:22:00",
